The story of two animals and their adventures. Milo, the cat, 
and Otis, the dog, are two animals who grew up together on the 
same farm. One day, the two are separated and begin a journey to 
find each other. The adventurous, and often perilous quest finds 
the two animals traveling across mountains, plains, and snow-covered 
lands searching for one another.
